fever on that night.

00:29:14.592 --> 00:29:15.074
AMAAN ALI BANGASH: Yeah.

00:29:15.074 --> 00:29:15.556
AYAAN ALI BANGASH: Yes.

00:29:15.556 --> 00:29:16.750
AMAAN ALI BANGASH: So
you know the pressures--

