you are on the right track.

00:31:20.940 --> 00:31:23.180
And I think you should be
OK-- or you will be OK.

00:31:23.180 --> 00:31:25.400
So faith in the
guru, faith in God.

00:31:25.400 --> 00:31:28.080
And it's hard work.

00:31:28.080 --> 00:31:29.800
And it's just a long way.

00:31:29.800 --> 00:31:32.990
We're starting a new
journey every day.

