sometimes, all night.

00:35:03.250 --> 00:35:05.090
And my father was
very, very old,

00:35:05.090 --> 00:35:09.020
because I was the youngest
child of their family.

00:35:09.020 --> 00:35:13.650
So I had elder
brothers and uncles.

00:35:13.650 --> 00:35:17.240
But the sense of
responsibility--

00:35:17.240 --> 00:35:20.590
for any child to realize
their responsibility

00:35:20.590 --> 00:35:23.262
is the greatest day
for the parents.

00:35:23.262 --> 00:35:25.800
So my father-- sometimes,
middle of the night,

00:35:25.800 --> 00:35:27.440
he saw me practicing--

00:35:27.440 --> 00:35:30.170
he will come and tell me,
[HINDI],, now go to sleep.

00:35:30.170 --> 00:35:31.840
So that was the father.

00:35:31.840 --> 00:35:35.330
But he was a hard
taskmaster while teaching.

00:35:35.330 --> 00:35:37.190
And he was very famous.

00:35:37.190 --> 00:35:39.350
He was very revered.

00:35:39.350 --> 00:35:41.735
And he got all the
awards and all that--

00:35:41.735 --> 00:35:45.980
but a saintly person,
committed to God

00:35:45.980 --> 00:35:48.670
and committed to
purity of music.

00:35:48.670 --> 00:35:50.170
SRIDHAR RAMASWAMY:
That's wonderful.

00:35:50.170 --> 00:35:50.878
That's wonderful.

