his musical approach.

00:36:47.570 --> 00:36:52.410
If you hear my father in the
'60s or in the '70s, '80s,

00:36:52.410 --> 00:36:55.760
'90s now, I think, there,
you can see a journey.

00:36:55.760 --> 00:36:59.291
