different thought process

00:36:59.291 --> 00:37:00.290
over the period of time.

00:37:00.290 --> 00:37:04.040
And today, my father's vision--

00:37:04.040 --> 00:37:06.440
I think he's playing
shorter pieces now.

00:37:06.440 --> 00:37:08.390
