bringing their game up.

00:42:35.520 --> 00:42:38.010
Because there's
more transparency.

00:42:38.010 --> 00:42:39.250
And it's a good thing.

00:42:39.250 --> 00:42:40.458
I think it was changing and--

00:42:40.458 --> 00:42:44.350
AMJAD ALI KHAN: But I think,
