00:42:56.300 --> 00:42:57.675
AMAAN ALI BANGASH:
Yeah, exactly.

00:42:57.675 --> 00:42:58.822
SRIDHAR RAMASWAMY: Right.

00:42:58.822 --> 00:43:00.280
AMJAD ALI KHAN:
Did you two think--

00:43:00.280 --> 00:43:03.760
actually, a great gift,
also, to all of us.

00:43:03.760 --> 00:43:07.100
And I'm proud of human beings
who have created mobile phones

00:43:07.100 --> 00:43:09.520
and iPads and all those--

00:43:09.520 --> 00:43:10.420
keyboard.

00:43:10.420 --> 00:43:13.540
The keyboard is a
amazing instrument

00:43:13.540 --> 00:43:18.310
that people can produce sound
