00:43:28.480 --> 00:43:32.950
But our music-- classical
music-- has been documented,

00:43:32.950 --> 00:43:33.714
because of digi--

00:43:33.714 --> 00:43:35.130
AYAAN ALI BANGASH:
Digitalization.

00:43:35.130 --> 00:43:36.000
AMAAN ALI BANGASH:
Digitalization.

00:43:36.000 --> 00:43:37.650
AMJAD ALI KHAN:
--digitalization.

00:43:37.650 --> 00:43:43.930
So because we cannot perform
identical next concert the way

00:43:43.930 --> 00:43:47.770
we play, whatever we
have played today--

00:43:47.770 --> 00:43:50.230
again, if we play
the same pieces,

00:43:50.230 --> 00:43:52.460
the expression
